{"tid":847770,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"【劈價升溫】名城四房低市價172萬易手","createTime":"2018-10-04T11:57:14.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-04T13:07:05.000Z","uid":174649,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"55ce1388b7b59432dbf7bcfa568ee71e9e72f34e","tid":847770,"uid":174649,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-04T11:57:14.000Z","msg":"加息後二手樓劈價升溫。消息指，大圍名城盛世3座高層NC室，實用面積958方呎，四房間隔，剛以1,828萬元沽出，呎價19,081元。位於今次成交單位同座樓上高層NC室，面積相同，今年6月造價2,000萬元，呎價20,877元，最新造價比數月前最癲峯價回落172萬元或8.6%。<br />\n<br />\n今年7月，盛世5座極低層NC室，實用面積1,042方呎，傳以2,150萬元透過買賣公司轉手，呎價20,633元，創出屋苑分層樓價新高。<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20181004/large/1538638825_ebca.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20181004%2Flarge%2F1538638825_ebca.jpg&h=7e2de3b6&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"764475be643491fea9896585a285c958a40ef5e4","tid":847770,"uid":171446,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-04T13:07:05.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"}]}